{"tid":1383476,"cid":27,"subCid":0,"title":"(教學) 仗，並唔係咁打架","createTime":"2019-07-29T16:50:38.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-30T02:27:43.000Z","uid":28648,"like":9,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"7ed75f6d92ba50a8b80400004aae0a28c443bd90","tid":1383476,"uid":28648,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T16:50:38.000Z","msg":"相信大家都有睇過 saving private ryan (雷霆救兵)，或者其他戰爭片。<br />\n<br />\n你地有無留意<span style=\"color: red;\">兵種</span>類別？<br />\n醫療兵，通訊兵，工兵，哨兵等等... <br />\n<br />\n除左兵種外，<span style=\"color: red;\">軍階</span>都好重要。<br />\n每一支軍隊，上至將軍，<br />\n下至 privaye ryan, 都係一層層傳遞信息。<br />\n<br />\n仲有 <span style=\"color: red;\">軍團組別</span>，<br />\n以 團/連/排 為一個單位，士兵以一定數量為一組。"},{"pid":"b656ec9f2808c24595ac0cb6dbba97f5a3c911df","tid":1383476,"uid":110851,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T16:52:16.000Z","msg":"打仗最重要係地圖<br />\n唔睇都埋嚟推下po<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n[集思廣益]香城online小地圖app<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1383244\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1383244</a>"},{"pid":"31acf3dea1322a16fe69167d396f3a59a243763d","tid":1383476,"uid":28648,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"quote":{"pid":"7ed75f6d92ba50a8b80400004aae0a28c443bd90","tid":1383476,"uid":28648,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T16:50:38.000Z","msg":"相信大家都有睇過 saving private ryan (雷霆救兵)，或者其他戰爭片。<br />\n<br />\n你地有無留意<span style=\"color: red;\">兵種</span>類別？<br />\n醫療兵，通訊兵，工兵，哨兵等等... <br />\n<br />\n除左兵種外，<span style=\"color: red;\">軍階</span>都好重要。<br />\n每一支軍隊，上至將軍，<br />\n下至 privaye ryan, 都係一層層傳遞信息。<br />\n<br />\n仲有 <span style=\"color: red;\">軍團組別</span>，<br />\n以 團/連/排 為一個單位，士兵以一定數量為一組。"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T16:55:06.000Z","msg":"以打 cs 為例，<br />\n<br />\n兵種其實做得唔錯：<br />\n醫療兵 已有<br />\n通訊兵 (旗手) 開始有<br />\n工兵 全部都係<br />\n哨兵 未有<br />\n<br />\n軍階：<br />\n暫時係無，人人皆兵，無大台，無指揮，全部以個人為中心，各自為戰<br />\n<br />\n組別方面：<br />\n最弱一環，唔見有系統性既組別分類"},{"pid":"6d9dc8840e95d0178c1add1eba767a40d5e5fbff","tid":1383476,"uid":28648,"like":6,"dislike":1,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T17:04:26.000Z","msg":"好喇，前言講左太多，我既建議係，<br />\n立即組隊打團戰, 以一定人數為一組，並且推舉位 leader.<br />\n<br />\n例：每組四十人<br />\n<br />\n團長（即時決策)：2人<br />\n醫療：1人<br />\n滅火：1人<br />\n通訊員 (負責同其他團溝通)：1人<br />\n物資員 (流動物資站）：5 人<br />\n其他工兵：30人<br />\n<br />\n可以分防務團，進攻團<br />\n<br />\n每個崗位只會帶自己崗位既裝備，而每個崗位可以唔同顏色做記認，如滅火用紅色閃燈，醫療用紅十字。"},{"pid":"e4d05bd0566f993bd08db6f995c1f84f65c20b43","tid":1383476,"uid":178684,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T17:05:54.000Z","msg":"先生/小姐，我而家跟據警察通例 Police General Orders 第20章 第14條要求你出示委任證，麻煩請你合作。<br />\n如果你無法出示委任證，根據香港法例第228章 第22條，我有合理理由懷疑你干犯假冒公職人員罪。<br />\n<br />\nRepeat 到佢出示委任證。"},{"pid":"6815711a3565151c7794465540a296bc2bdc3182","tid":1383476,"uid":28648,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T17:06:07.000Z","msg":"最後，配以鍵盤戰士做網上軍師"},{"pid":"c5fe80e785c66e83784cc6d06236ef59e66dcac1","tid":1383476,"uid":28648,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T17:31:37.000Z","msg":"大家有無野講？<br />\n我無野講"},{"pid":"0b04a36c11f84e701eb98c69b48ed6eaa47107be","tid":1383476,"uid":151040,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T17:32:35.000Z","msg":"阻阻大家 開左個整合post <br />\n幫幫手report d藍絲 保護前線<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n[整合］［後勤戰士急入］<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1383387\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1383387</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"0446057850cab8d97db60677f61166620f73b21e","tid":1383476,"uid":187537,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"cite